{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.840", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.440", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich bin das letzte Mal schon gew\u00fcrdigt worden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.280", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.600", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.320", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Arbeitszeitgesetz l\u00e4sst schon jetzt zahlreiche Ausnahmen zu. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.480", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn ein Gesetz nicht starr ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.840", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann ist es das Arbeitszeitgesetz."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.080", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn eine Mutter von 8.30\u00a0Uhr bis 15\u00a0Uhr arbeitet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.080", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann ihre Kinder abholt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.320", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Nachmittag mit ihnen verbringt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.600", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sie zum Turnen f\u00e4hrt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.600", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ins Bett bringt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.880", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die liegen n\u00e4mlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.520", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil sie vom Turnen fix und fertig sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.760", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um halb acht im Bett\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.240", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann kann sie locker noch bis halb zehn arbeiten und am n\u00e4chsten Morgen wieder um 8.30\u00a0Uhr anfangen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.800", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Alles das ist mit unserem Arbeitszeitgesetz \u00fcberhaupt kein Problem. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.960", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was verboten ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.320", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.400", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie die Nacht durcharbeitet und morgens um 7\u00a0Uhr wieder auf der Matte steht\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.960", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das ist auch gut so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.280", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das verboten ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.480", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Warum gibt es \u00fcberhaupt diese Schutzrechte? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.880", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Weil es im Verh\u00e4ltnis zwischen Besch\u00e4ftigten und Arbeitgebern eben nicht automatisch zu einem Interessenausgleich kommt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.320", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und weil es eben nicht um das einmalige E-Mail-Schreiben um 23\u00a0Uhr geht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.320", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielmehr zeigt die Erfahrung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.880", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Abbau von Schutzrechten von Arbeitgeberseite immer zulasten der Besch\u00e4ftigten ausgenutzt wurde."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.120", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Trotzdem: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.040", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Welt \u00e4ndert sich und so auch die Arbeitswelt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.520", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen ist die Frage nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.560", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob man Schutzrechte f\u00fcr Arbeitnehmerinnen und Arbeitnehmer abbaut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.480", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.200", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie man Altes ver\u00e4ndert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.640", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber vielleicht auch neue Rechte f\u00fcr die Arbeitnehmer schafft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.120", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen wollen wir das in Experimentierr\u00e4umen zeitlich und inhaltlich begrenzt erproben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.920", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wissenschaftlich begleiten und evaluieren"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.000", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und aus den daraus gewonnenen Erfahrungen m\u00f6glichst eine Erneuerung und Modernisierung der Schutzrechte f\u00fcr die Arbeitnehmerinnen und Arbeitnehmer entwickeln."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.920", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn man aber wirklich mehr Freiheit f\u00fcr die Menschen bei der Gestaltung ihrer Arbeitszeit und bei der Organisation ihres Lebens m\u00f6chte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.520", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann muss man sich um die Vereinbarkeit von Familie und Beruf k\u00fcmmern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.520", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zum Beispiel durch bessere und flexiblere Betreuungsangebote. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.880", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das haben wir getan, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.000", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das tun wir auch weiterhin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.200", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "indem wir das Recht auf Ganztagsbetreuung auch im Grundschulalter einr\u00e4umen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.080", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann muss man auch das R\u00fcckkehrrecht in Vollzeit schaffen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.120", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch das schaffen wir. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.360", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann braucht man Elternzeit und Elterngeld; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.360", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das haben wir. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.640", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann braucht man die M\u00f6glichkeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.800", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch die Pflege der Eltern zu organisieren; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.600", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das haben wir mit dem Pflegeunterst\u00fctzungsgeld und der Pflegezeit erleichtert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.360", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und man braucht eine Familienarbeitszeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.560", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die es erm\u00f6glicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.520", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Arbeitszeit zu reduzieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.680", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch wenn man nicht zu den Besserverdienenden geh\u00f6rt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.680", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen das Leben der Menschen leichter machen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.440", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dazu haben wir auch in dieser Koalition viel vor. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.680", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich m\u00f6chte Coco Chanel zitieren\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.680", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das habe ich hier noch nie gemacht; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.360", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber irgendwie passt es\u00a0\u2013:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.720", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt eine Zeit f\u00fcr die Arbeit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.680", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und es gibt eine Zeit f\u00fcr die Liebe. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.160", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mehr Zeit hat man nicht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.160", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Also lassen Sie uns sorgsam mit dieser Zeit umgehen!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.480", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielleicht kann man dieses Zitat ins Protokoll in Fettdruck aufnehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.120", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich schreibe es mir auf jeden Fall auf.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.040", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.440", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Schmidt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.320", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Letzter Redner in der Debatte: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.360", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Stephan Stracke f\u00fcr die CDU/CSU-Fraktion. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.960", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist jetzt die andere Stimme aus dem Kaufbeurer Allg\u00e4u."
   ]
  }
 ]
